---
import Container from "./Container.astro"

---

<div id="blog">
  <Container>
      <div class="mb-12 space-y-2 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl dark:text-white">Latest Features</h2>
        <p class="lg:mx-auto lg:w-6/12 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          Discover our newest sustainability and cost optimization features that help you reduce both infrastructure costs and environmental impact
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="group p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 dark:shadow-none dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-50 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10">
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
            <img src="https://docs.ksctl.com/img/blogs/new_selection_instance_type.png"
            alt="Smart Region and Instance Selection" loading="lazy" class="h-64 w-full object-cover object-top transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"/>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 relative">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
              v2.5: Smart Region and Instance Selection
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                This intelligent feature guides you in selecting the optimal region and instance type for your clusters by analyzing both emissions data and cost efficiency. It automatically ranks potential choices based on carbon intensity, renewable power percentage, and overall cost.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
              <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded dark:bg-green-900 dark:text-green-300">
                Emission Optimization
              </span>
              <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded dark:bg-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300">
                Cost Efficiency
              </span>
              <span class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded dark:bg-amber-900 dark:text-amber-300">
                Embodied Emissions
              </span>
            </div>
            <a class="inline-block mt-4" href="https://docs.ksctl.com/blog/2025/04/13/ksctl-v2.5-smart-region-and-instance-selection/">
              <span class="text-primary dark:text-secondary hover:underline">Learn more →</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="group p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 dark:shadow-none dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-50 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10">
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
            <img src="https://docs.ksctl.com/img/blogs/ksctl-new-recommendation.png"
            alt="Dynamic Region Switching" loading="lazy" class="h-64 w-full object-cover object-top transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"/>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 relative">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
              v2.4: Dynamic Region Switching
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                Dynamic Region Switching intelligently selects the most sustainable and cost-effective region for your Kubernetes clusters, minimizing expenses and emissions while maintaining the same instance type.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
              <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded dark:bg-green-900 dark:text-green-300">
                Carbon Reduction
              </span>
              <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded dark:bg-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300">
                Automatic Optimization
              </span>
              <span class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded dark:bg-amber-900 dark:text-amber-300">
                Renewable Energy
              </span>
            </div>
            <a class="inline-block mt-4" href="https://docs.ksctl.com/blog/2025/04/10/ksctl-v2.4-smarter-optimization-with-dynamic-region-switching/">
                <span class="text-primary dark:text-secondary hover:underline">Learn more →</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </Container>
</div>